{"tid":1982060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［賺到笑］比亞迪獲美國加州10億美元口罩訂單","createTime":"2020-04-21T04:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T04:43:57.000Z","uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7709618b3e4d2e4903ca3c24dda3fd68c96f09b4","tid":1982060,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T04:15:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2623222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2623222&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBidRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=7b5ec6f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2623222</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金融經濟 10:52 2020/04/21  <br />\n<br />\n▲ 比亞迪將向美國加州出口價值10億美元的口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全球新冠肺炎疫情持續下，口罩需求有增無減。比亞迪（01211）近日獲美國加州約10億美元（約77.5億港元）的口罩訂單。比亞迪早前獲美國食品藥物監管局（FDA）下批緊急使用權（EUA），可出口口罩至美國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此外，日本軟銀集團創始人孫正義早前與比亞迪達成協議。5月開始，比亞迪將每月向軟銀集團出售3個隻口罩，包括1億個常規醫用外科口罩及1億個醫用N95口罩。"},{"pid":"13871181e0cd854384c8d54782acaeb5400b3f1d","tid":1982060,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"美國越病，支那越有米 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01aba95c7df27d88aa9a895943813ac863696d5c","tid":1982060,"uid":62151,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T04:21:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">比亞迪（01211）近日獲美國<span style=\"color: red;\">加州</span>約10億美元（約77.5億港元）的口罩訂單。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://thyblackman.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/democrat.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthyblackman.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fdemocrat.jpg&h=9c28aafd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"917eca3154564a2c8aad4cb653527ec3bd389885","tid":1982060,"uid":181502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T04:43:57.000Z","msg":"比亞迪返去整軍用車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一去到敵人陣地炸死幾百人嗰啲"}]}